    {"id":8,"question":"연립방정식 $\\begin{cases} y = x + 1 \\\\ y = -2x + 7 \\end{cases}$의 해는?","choices":["$(2, 3)$","$(3, 2)$","$(1, 2)$","$(7, 8)$","$(0, 1)$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$x+1=-2x+7$ → $3x=6$ → $x=2$, $y=3$"},
